**Problem 2.1** Suppose $|ϵ_i| ≤ ϵ$ and $n ϵ < 1$. Show that
$$
∏_{k=1}^n (1+ϵ_i) = 1+θ_n
$$
for some constant $θ_n$ satisfying
$$
|θ_n| ≤ \underbrace{n ϵ \over 1-nϵ}_{E_{n,ϵ}}
$$
Hint: use induction.



